og-listing-header__divider"><ul class="blog-listing-header__meta"><li class="blog-listing-header__meta__item"><a href="/plugged-in/about/">About</a></li><li class="blog-listing-header__meta__item"><a href="http://rss.sciam.com/plugged-in/feed">RSS</a></li></ul></div></header><div class="landing-main"><div class="container"><div class="grid sticky-bounds"><div class="grid__col large-up-8-12 paginated-article-list"><article class="listing-wide" data-listing-template="Blog" data-listing-title="<i>Plugged In</i> Says Farewell"><div class="listing-wide__thumb " ><a href="https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/plugged-in/plugged-in-says-farewell/"><picture><source media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="https://static.scientificamerican.com/blogs/cache/file/BECE1151-E612-4EE3-B6009808AD86E491_small.jpg"><source media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px)" srcset="https://static.scientificamerican.com/blogs/cache/file/BECE1151-E612-4EE3-B6009808AD86E491_medium.jpg?w=210&amp;h=140&fit=crop"><img src="https://static.scientificamerican.com/blogs/cache/file/BECE1151-E612-4EE3-B6009808AD86E491_agenda.jpg?w=275&h=154&amp;fit=crop" alt="&lt;i&gt;Plugged In&lt;/i&gt; Says Farewell"></picture><div class="t_tag listing-wide__thumb__category">Energy</div></a></div><div class="listing-wide__inner"><h2 class="t_listing-title"><a href="https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/plugged-in/plugged-in-says-farewell/">"Plugged In" Says Farewell</a></h2><p class="t_body listing-wide__inner__desc"><em>Plugged In</em> will unplug on Friday. It&rsquo;s been a great seven years and we look forward to continuing the conversations that we started here</p><div class="t_meta">June 6, 2018 &mdash; Robert Fares, Sheril Kirshenbaum, Melissa C. Lott and Tali Trigg</div></div></article><article class="listing-wide" data-listing-template="Blog" data-listing-title="Making Electricity Consumes a Lot of Water--What's the Best Way to Fix That?"><div class="listing-wide__thumb " ><a href="https://blogs.scientificame