le/96A3351E-C33C-4262-92A9D453158A0882_small.jpg?w=65&h=65" alt="Dog Spies" /></div><h3 class="listing-blog-index__title"><span class="ellipsis listing-blog-index__underline">Dog Spies</span></h3><p class="listing-blog-index__summary">Explore the science behind the dog in your bed</p><a href="https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/dog-spies/" class="listing-blog-index__link">Read</a></article></div></section></li>	<li><section class="grid"><div class="grid__col large-up-1-2" data-blog-title="Extinction Countdown"><article class="listing-blog-index"><div class="listing-blog-index__icon"><img src="https://static.scientificamerican.com/blogs/cache/file/D3C0CF11-8204-4C7D-A89FDDF308736736_small.jpg?w=65&h=65" alt="Extinction Countdown" /></div><h3 class="listing-blog-index__title"><span class="ellipsis listing-blog-index__underline">Extinction Countdown</span></h3><p class="listing-blog-index__summary">News and research about endangered species from around the world</p><a href="https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/extinction-countdown/" class="listing-blog-index__link">Read</a></article></div><div class="grid__col large-up-1-2" data-blog-title="Eye of the Storm"><article class="listing-blog-index"><div class="listing-blog-index__icon"><img src="https://static.scientificamerican.com/blogs/cache/file/31A82CAB-AE50-4D83-972E8CEEF09875C3_small.png?w=65&h=65" alt="Eye of the Storm" /></div><h3 class="listing-blog-index__title"><span class="ellipsis listing-blog-index__underline">Eye of the Storm</span></h3><p class="listing-blog-index__summary">The Science Behind Extreme Weather</p><a href="https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/eye-of-the-storm/" class="listing-blog-index__link">Read</a></article></div><div class="grid__col large-up-1-2" data-blog-title="Frontiers for Young Minds"><article class="listing-blog-index"><div class="listing-blog-index__icon"><img src="https://static.scientificamerican.com/blogs/cache/file/D80F20BD-80FA-4C47-92CC2C6BB1B5A7CB_small.jpg?w=65&h=65" alt=